articles.title: Bodies found as Mexican police discover tents, question people in case of San Diego man, 2 Australians missing in Baja - KABC-TV
articles.description: Bodies have been found near a burned truck as Mexican authorities discovered tents and questioned three people in the case of two Australians and an American who went missing in Baja California.
articles.content: MEXICO CITY -- Mexican authorities said Thursday they have found tents and questioned three people in the case of two Australians and an American who went missing over the weekend in the Pacific coas… [+2921 chars]
